  Usage:
  # Full aggregation
  uv run python -m ai_services.scripts.experiments.control_detection.reason_aggregator.run --all

  # Lower parallelism
  uv run python -m ai_services.scripts.experiments.control_detection.reason_aggregator.run --all -n 2

  # Single round
  uv run python -m ai_services.scripts.experiments.control_detection.reason_aggregator.run --round 1

  # Resume interrupted run
  uv run python -m ai_services.scripts.experiments.control_detection.reason_aggregator.run --all --resume

  # Dry run to see plan
  uv run python -m ai_services.scripts.experiments.control_detection.reason_aggregator.run --all --dry-run

  The Map-Reduce Reason Aggregator is now complete and ready for use!